---js
const layout = "layouts/home.njk";
const title = "Freelance Web Developer Berlin";
const description = "Matt Richards — freelance senior+ web, frontend and software engineer in Berlin. Twenty years in. Product engineering and engineering leadership for ambitious teams.";
---
{% css %}
@layer page {
	main {
		display: block;
	}

	.freelance {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 80ch;
		margin-inline: auto;
		padding-inline: clamp(var(--space-s), 4vw, var(--space-l));
		padding-block: var(--space-l) var(--space-3xl);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		row-gap: var(--space-2xl);
	}

	@media (min-width: 1200px) {
		.freelance { max-width: 90ch; }
	}

	/* Breadcrumb */
	.freelance-crumbs {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.22em;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		color: var(--fg-quiet);
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.6em;
	}

	.freelance-crumbs a {
		color: inherit;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
		padding-bottom: 0.1em;
	}

	.freelance-crumbs a:hover { opacity: 0.65; }
	.freelance-crumbs .sep { opacity: 0.45; }

	/* Hero */
	.freelance-hero {
		max-width: 60ch;
	}

	.freelance-eyebrow {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.22em;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		color: var(--fg-subtle);
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75em;
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-s);
	}

	.freelance-eyebrow::before {
		content: "";
		width: 2.5em;
		height: 1px;
		background: currentColor;
	}

	.freelance-hero h1 {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		font-weight: 900;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
		line-height: 0.9;
		letter-spacing: -0.015em;
		color: var(--fg);
		margin: 0;
		text-wrap: balance;
	}

	.freelance-hero h1 em {
		font-style: normal;
		display: inline-block;
		position: relative;
		color: var(--fg);
	}

	.freelance-hero h1 em::before {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		left: -0.05em;
		right: -0.05em;
		top: 0.35em;
		bottom: 0.15em;
		background: var(--accent);
		z-index: -1;
	}

	.freelance-hero .lede {
		font-size: clamp(var(--step-0), 0.8vw + 0.95rem, var(--step-1));
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--fg-muted);
		max-width: 52ch;
		margin: var(--space-m) 0 0;
		text-wrap: pretty;
	}

	.freelance-meta {
		margin-top: var(--space-m);
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: var(--space-s) var(--space-m);
		align-items: baseline;
	}

	.freelance-meta .eyebrow-link {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
		padding-bottom: 0.2em;
	}

	.freelance-meta .eyebrow-link::after { content: "  →"; }
	.freelance-meta .eyebrow-link:hover { opacity: 0.65; }

	.freelance-locator {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		color: var(--fg-muted);
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5em;
	}

	/* Service strip */
	.freelance-services {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
	}

	.service {
		padding: var(--space-m);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-3xs);
		border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}
	.service:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
	.service:last-child  { padding-right: 0; border-right: 0; }

	.service-kicker {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		color: var(--fg-quiet);
	}

	.service-head {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: var(--step-1);
		line-height: 1;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
		margin: 0.1em 0 0.2em;
		color: var(--fg);
	}

	.service-body {
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		color: var(--fg-muted);
		line-height: 1.45;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 32ch;
	}

	/* Body sections */
	.freelance-section {
		max-width: 64ch;
		margin-inline: auto;
		padding-block: var(--space-l) 0;
	}

	.freelance-section + .freelance-section {
		margin-top: var(--space-m);
		padding-top: var(--space-l);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}

	.freelance-section h2 {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		font-weight: 900;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem);
		line-height: 0.95;
		letter-spacing: -0.005em;
		color: var(--fg);
		margin: 0 0 var(--space-m);
	}

	.freelance-section h2 .ix {
		display: block;
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		font-weight: 400;
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		letter-spacing: 0.25em;
		color: var(--fg-quiet);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-s);
	}

	.freelance-body {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-m);
	}

	.freelance-body p {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.65;
		font-size: var(--step-0);
		color: var(--fg);
		text-wrap: pretty;
	}

	.freelance-body ul {
		list-style: none;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		display: grid;
		gap: var(--space-xs);
	}

	.freelance-body li {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.6em;
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: var(--fg);
	}

	.freelance-body li::before {
		content: "§";
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0;
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		color: var(--fg-quiet);
		line-height: inherit;
	}

	.freelance-body li strong {
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.freelance-body a {
		color: inherit;
		text-underline-offset: 0.2em;
	}

	/* Next up */
	.freelance-next {
		margin-top: var(--space-l);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
	}

	.next {
		padding: var(--space-m);
		border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: var(--space-2xs);
	}
	.next:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
	.next:last-child  { padding-right: 0; border-right: 0; }

	.next-kicker {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.18em;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		color: var(--fg-quiet);
	}

	.next h3 {
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: var(--step-1);
		line-height: 1;
		letter-spacing: 0.01em;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--fg);
	}

	.next p {
		font-size: var(--step--1);
		color: var(--fg-muted);
		line-height: 1.45;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 28ch;
	}

	.next a.cta {
		margin-top: var(--space-2xs);
		font-family: var(--feature-font);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		font-size: var(--step--2);
		text-decoration: none;
		border-bottom: 1px solid currentColor;
		padding-bottom: 0.2em;
		align-self: start;
		color: inherit;
	}
	.next a.cta::after { content: "  →"; }
	.next a.cta:hover { opacity: 0.65; }

	/* Narrow viewports */
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.freelance-hero h1 {
			font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 11vw, 3.5rem);
		}

		.freelance-services,
		.freelance-next {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.service,
		.next {
			border-right: 0;
			border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
			padding-inline: 0;
		}
		.service:last-child,
		.next:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
		@keyframes freelance-rise-in {
			from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(0.4rem); }
			to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
		}

		.freelance > * {
			animation: 650ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both freelance-rise-in;
		}

		.freelance > :nth-child(1) { animation-delay:   0ms; }
		.freelance > :nth-child(2) { animation-delay:  80ms; }
		.freelance > :nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 180ms; }
		.freelance > :nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 280ms; }
		.freelance > :nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 380ms; }
		.freelance > :nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 480ms; }
	}
}
{% endcss %}

<article class="freelance">
	<nav class="freelance-crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
		<a href="/">Home</a>
		<span class="sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
		<span aria-current="page">Freelance</span>
	</nav>

	<header class="freelance-hero">
		<p class="freelance-eyebrow">Matt Richards &middot; Berlin</p>
		<h1>Freelance web developer. <em>Berlin.</em></h1>
		<p class="lede">Senior+ product engineer for hire &mdash; web, frontend, full-stack. Twenty years in, based in Berlin, working with teams across Germany, the EU and remote. Freelance software engineering and engineering leadership for ambitious products.</p>
		<div class="freelance-meta">
			<a class="eyebrow-link" href="/contact">Start a conversation</a>
			<span class="freelance-locator"><span class="online-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>Currently open to new work</span>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="freelance-services" aria-label="Services">
		<div class="service">
			<span class="service-kicker">&sect; 01</span>
			<h2 class="service-head">Freelance frontend</h2>
			<p class="service-body">React, TypeScript, modern CSS. Accessible, performant interfaces that hold up outside a demo. Design systems that stay coherent as they grow.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="service">
			<span class="service-kicker">&sect; 02</span>
			<h2 class="service-head">Freelance full-stack</h2>
			<p class="service-body">End-to-end product engineering on the web: DOM to database, Node or BFF, the unglamorous middle where most product value actually lives.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="service">
			<span class="service-kicker">&sect; 03</span>
			<h2 class="service-head">Engineering lead</h2>
			<p class="service-body">Fractional engineering leadership, architecture reviews, team shape and hiring. The judgement calls that are hard to make from inside the org.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="freelance-section">
		<h2><span class="ix">&sect; 04 &mdash; What I'm for</span>The engagements that fit</h2>
		<div class="freelance-body">
			<p>I work best with product teams that take the web platform seriously and want an engineer who can move between code, architecture and leadership without needing a translator. I'm based in Berlin and available across the EU and remote.</p>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Freelance senior frontend engineer</strong> &mdash; embedded on a product team, shipping features and levelling the rest of the frontend craft while I'm there.</li>
				<li><strong>Freelance full-stack / software engineer</strong> &mdash; owning a product surface end-to-end, TypeScript top to bottom, Node or an adjacent stack.</li>
				<li><strong>Fractional engineering lead</strong> &mdash; technical strategy, roadmap shape, org design, hiring, mentorship. Close to the work, out of the team's way.</li>
				<li><strong>Architecture &amp; codebase review</strong> &mdash; honest read on what's load-bearing, what's rot, and what's worth the rewrite.</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="freelance-section">
		<h2><span class="ix">&sect; 05 &mdash; How I work</span>Fundamentals, first.</h2>
		<div class="freelance-body">
			<p>Platform-first. HTML, CSS and the DOM before any framework. SOLID principles, clean boundaries, appropriate coupling, systems that stay coherent as they grow. Accessibility and UX as defaults, not retrofits.</p>
			<p>AI is part of how I build now &mdash; used every day, kept on a short leash. Keeping humans, products and codebases healthy in the age of AI is the engineering problem of the decade, and I've thought about it a lot. <a href="/about">More about how I work &rarr;</a></p>
			<p>I write about this &mdash; craft, leadership, and keeping codebases humane &mdash; on <a href="/words">the words archive</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="freelance-next" aria-label="Where to go next">
		<div class="next">
			<span class="next-kicker">Background</span>
			<h3>About</h3>
			<p>Twenty years, two sides of the bench: product engineering and engineering leadership.</p>
			<a class="cta" href="/about">Read the long version</a>
		</div>
		<div class="next">
			<span class="next-kicker">Writing</span>
			<h3>Words</h3>
			<p>Notes on craft, leadership, and the age of AI. The archive &mdash; dated, unvarnished.</p>
			<a class="cta" href="/words">Open the archive</a>
		</div>
		<div class="next">
			<span class="next-kicker">Work together</span>
			<h3>Contact</h3>
			<p>Email, Signal, or the form. Tell me what you're building and what's in the way.</p>
			<a class="cta" href="/contact">Get in touch</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</article>

<script type="application/ld+json">
